<AbsText HTMLContent="true">          &lt;html&gt;            &lt;head&gt;              &lt;meta name="ValidationSchema" content="http://www.w3.org/2002/08/xhtml/xhtml1-strict.xsd"/&gt;              &lt;title/&gt;            &lt;/head&gt;            &lt;body&gt;              &lt;p&gt;[...]why, except that he looked Hispanic, would the officer have asked for his papers?  [...]how likely is it that Hispanic-looking folks will be pulled over for "suspicious behavior" for the sole purpose of checking those papers?&lt;/p&gt;            &lt;/body&gt;          &lt;/html&gt;</AbsText>
